snippet.title: de Blob DS (Unreleased Gameplay)
snippet.description: What your looking at is never before scene gameplay of the Nintendo DS version of de Blob 1. This footage was shown off by Rebeltaxi on twitter as appearently someone gave it to him. While de Blob 1 never got a Nintendo DS release it's sequal did. Now we just have to wait until someone leaks Syfy's cancelled de Blob Cartoon.
